Say '''Bulusan''' et kumapat ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Sorsogon]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 22,089 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 96.3 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumadwa ya distrito. Say zip code to et 4704.	
															
